room_title: Escape room "Blackbeard's Quarters" by Ctrl Shift Escape in Greenville (NC)
room_address: 4051 South Memorial Dr # C1 Winterville NC 28590
room_description: Blackbeard has stolen gold from other pirates off the coast of North Carolina. You've snuck on board of the ship to try and retrieve the treasure. You must make your way out of the Captain's Quarters before the crew finds you and makes you walk the plank!
